    IBaseContract

    public static interface IBaseContract.IBasePresenter<IView extends IBaseContract.IBaseView>

    • 方法详细资料

      • onAttach

        void onAttach(android.content.Context context)
        save context for some initialization depending on context.
        参数:
        context - the activity's context passing to presenter while fragment is attached to activity

      • onCreate

        void onCreate(android.os.Bundle savedInfo)
        Initialize presenter with saved information in Bundle. Start some timer or thread job for all but not UI.
        参数:
        savedInfo - passing from activity

      • onStart

        void onStart(IView view)
        Bind IBaseView to IBasePresenter, and start some timer or thread job for UI.
        参数:
        view - sub-class of BaseFragment in MyMvp framework

      • onResume

        void onResume()
        view is on foreground, and presenter can update view now.

      • onPause

        void onPause()
        view is going to be covered by other UI, save some information if needed.

      • onStop

        void onStop()
        stop some timer or thread job for UI, and unbind IBaseView from IBasePresenter.

      • onSaveState

        void onSaveState(android.os.Bundle savedInfo)
        save some information into 'savedInfo' for showing next time if needed. such as filter information, process percentage, and so on.
        参数:
        savedInfo - passing from activity

      • onDestroy

        void onDestroy()
        stop some timer or thread job for all. release all memory which are no need to be kept on.

      • onDetach

        void onDetach()
        context is not available, and do left finalization

      • onSaveListener

        boolean onSaveListener(java.lang.Object one,
                       boolean isNew)
        the listener for user saving operation
        参数:
        one - the data that user wants to save, whose class type must be one BaseModel's T type
        isNew - true for adding and false fo modifying
        返回:
        true for request sent successfully, or else false

      • onDeleteListener

        boolean onDeleteListener(java.lang.Object one)
        the listener for user deleting operation
        参数:
        one - the data that user wants to delete, whose class type must be one BaseModel's T type Most of time it's only with a valid ID part.
        返回:
        true for request sent successfully, or else false
